      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely pristine! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a quick sale to a good home. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
