    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S, a definitive example of the 997.1 chassis in museum-grade condition. This specimen is powered by the 3.8L M97.01 flat-six, featuring an optimized power-to-weight ratio and a linear torque curve. The drivetrain is anchored by a G97/01 6-speed manual transaxle with a factory-spec short-throw shifter for precise gate engagement. Mechanical highlights include a documented IMS solution, zero bore scoring, and a fully functional Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system. The chassis remains rigid with no subframe oxidation, while the factory-applied finish and interior upholstery show no signs of UV degradation or mechanical wear. This is a turn-key, concours-ready machine for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
