    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained to satisfy the most discerning collector. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its deep factory brilliance with no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, preserved under a multi-layer ceramic coating. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple without a single crease or bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since delivery. Every technological feature, sensor, and button operates with crisp, factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance condition, backed by a comprehensive, chronological service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is a single-owner vehicle with a clean title, complete with all original keys, manuals, and documentation. I welcome and encourage a third-party pre-purchase inspection to confirm that this vehicle is as perfect as described.",
